News.headline: 50/50 Draw Solihull Moors
News.short_description: The Winner for the Daggers' Vanarama National League game versus Solihull Moors is ticket number 04579.
News.description:
The winning ticket worth £200.00 was drawn at half time. The winning ticket was claimed by D. Tresadern.

Second place winner for the £50 Johnstone's Paint voucher is ticket number 04657, which was claimed by Helen Swann.

The third place winner for the copy of Football Manager 2017 (PC) is ticket number 04556, this prize is yet to be claimed.

50/50 tickets can be purchased on match days for £1.
